			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of Fischer Schaechter on his deportation from Hungary to Ukraine in 1942 and his return. He was sent to the Nagyszollos Ghetto and later deported to Auschwitz, where he and his twin brother served as guinea pigs for medical experiments.</p>
			</abstract>
